}

#watch-discussion,
#watch7-sidebar-contents,
#masthead {
    background-color: #0b000a61 !important;
    border-color: #0ff !important;
}


::selection {
    background: #55ffe9 !important;
    color: #008080 !important;
}
::-moz-selection {
    background: #0ff !important;
    color: #000 !important;
}

.html5-play-progress,
.ytp-play-progress {
    background: url("data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAAMCAYAAACji9dXAAAABmJLR0QAAACAAID1ziPfAAAACXBIWXMAAC4jAAAuIwF4pT92AAAARUlEQVQI1wXBIQ7AIBREwZdVKARcgDNUcX/TIHBNBYKkOJKK7xEww2+29c2J7tZQGQNVM/SuhQCUnUNXjCinBE/vW8F7DkBWFek7KKZIAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC") repeat-x !important;
    background: linear-gradient(to top,
    #000 1%,
    #0ff 10%,
    #008080 34%,
    #008080 38%,
    #0080807d 61%,
    #a900cf85 89%,
    #000 99%) !important;

    background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top,
    #000 1%,
    #0ff 10%,
    #008080 34%,
    #008080 38%,
    #0080807d 61%,
    #a900cf85 89%,
    #000 99%) !important;

    background: -moz-linear-gradient(top,
    #000 1%,
    #0ff 10%,
    #008080 34%,
    #008080 38%,
    #008080 61%,
    #a900cf 89%,
    #000 99%) !important;
}


.html5-load-progress,
.ytp-load-progress {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient( 270deg,
    #00ffff6e,
    #00ffff6e 20px,
    #000 20px,
    #00000073 40px);

    background-size: 600% 100%;
    animation: gradient 700s linear infinite!important;
    animation-direction: alternate-reverse;

    /*
    background:  url("data:image/gif;base64,") !important;
    */
}

.html5-scrubber-button,
.ytp-scrubber-button {
    background: url("data:image/png;base64,") !important;
    width: 18px !important;
    height: 18px !important;
    border: none !important;
    margin-left: 0px !important;
    margin-top: 0px !important;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 3px #f0f;
}
.ytp-progress-bar-container:hover .ytp-scrubber-button,
.ytp-progress-bar-container:hover .ytp-load-progress {
    image-rendering: smooth;
}
.html5-progress-bar-container,
.ytp-progress-bar-container {
    height: 10px !important;
}
.html5-progress-bar,
.ytp-progress-bar {
    margin-top: 10px !important;
}
.html5-progress-list,
.ytp-progress-list,
.video-ads .html5-progress-list.html5-ad-progress-list,
.video-ads .ytp-progress-list.ytp-ad-progress-list {
    height: 8px !important;
}
.ytp-volume-slider-track {
    background: #0ff !important;
}

@keyframes gradient {
    0% {
        background-position: 0%
    }
    100% {
        background-position: 100%
    }
}

@keyframes grow {
    0% {
        size: 0;
    }
    100% {
        size: 500%;
    }
}

@keyframes fadein {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
        opacity: 0.5;
    }
}

@keyframes lights {
    0% {
        background-position: 0% 11%
    }
    50% {
        background-position: 100% 90%
    }
    100% {
        background-position: 0% 11%
    }
}
}
